latestPosts.caption:
And she finally met herself. Not in some big, dramatic moment, but in the little things. In the way she smiled at her reflection instead of picking herself apart. In the way she let herself rest without feeling guilty. In the way she started choosing what made her happy, not what made her fit in.She realized that selflove wasn’t about being perfect, it was about being kind to herself. It was about speaking to herself the way she’d speak to someone she loves. It was about knowing that no amount of external validation could fill the space she hadn’t filled for herself. And once she truly loved herself, she saw love differently. She no longer searched for someone to complete her, she was already whole.🤍

#lovingyourself #beyou #prioratiseyourself #relatable #selflove
It was all yellow💛💐
